column5: I no i am ...  the river froze hard last night when i walked out goose hunting the ice was spongy when i came back off the river in the dark it was rock hard ..last night we had -7 here made for better ice ..ill report on the eyes late tonight ..if anybody wants to get out ice fishing do it Saturday Sunday is going to be wettttttt
Im heading for south bay tommorow
I will be out for sure.
I got skunked for splake last night and did some math...  rain this weekend=rainbows  luck everyone
Thier's upose to be a melt down on the weekend, and not having a floater suite I'll wait till it gets backin the minus teens.
